room_title: Escape room "Hollywood Dreams" by Escape Room Long Beach in Los Angeles
room_address: 3605 Long Beach Boulevard Suite 304 Long Beach, CA 90807
room_description:
Hollywood is hard enough to break into for aspiring screenwriters. It’s an impossible mission when jerk directors are passing off your script as their own. Well, you’re not going to let him get away with it!
You’re sneaking into his office to get your script back. He’s out to lunch. You’ve paid off the secretary. Now just find your script and get out before he gets back. Or get caught, and watch your dreams sink faster than the Titanic.
Hey, this is sounding like a pretty good movie already…
